--- /1/droid/_mkimg/u-boot/configs/nanopi_m1_plus_defconfig     2018-02-11 11:54:50.187073295 +0100

 # CONFIG_SYS_MALLOC_CLEAR_ON_INIT is not set
 CONFIG_SPL=y
